<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạsm rby brjy ạlḥṣyn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạsmu rabĩya bur̊jīa ạl̊ḥaṣīn̊
 ṭūla ʿum̊rīa bihi ạảs̊taʿīn̊
 hūa ṣakẖ̊ratī was̊ṭa ạảḥ̊zānī
 yā lagẖib̊ṭatī hūa miʿ̊wānī

[V2]
 2- fī dujay̱ ạlẓãlạm̊ hūa lī rafīq̊
 waj̊huhu ạl̊basãạm̊ mur̊sẖidu ạlṭãrīq̊
 qal̊buhu ạlrãqīq̊ dāyỉmu ạl̊ḥanān̊
 ạ̹nh ạlrafīq̊ mā ṭāla ạlzãmān̊

[V3]
 3- fī balạyānā kadẖā wāl̊kẖuṭūb̊
 yaḥ̊milu ạl̊ʿanā yun̊jidu ạl̊magẖ̊lūb̊
 hal̊ lahu matẖīl̊ sayĩdī ạl̊masīḥ̊
 ại̹nãhu ạl̊kẖalīl̊ bihi ạảs̊tarīḥ̊

[V4]
 4- sabĩḥīhi yā sẖam̊su yā ạảq̊mār̊
 yā samāʾu yā ạảr̊ḍu yā biḥār̊
 bārikūạ ạs̊mahu yā banī ạlại̹ymān̊
 yā junūdahu ại̹nãhu ạl̊manãạn̊</lyrics>
</song>